summary: An ordinance relating to and amending Plat 78W & 78E, page 183 & 184, of the Official Zoning Map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in South Park Addition, Lots 29 to 48 incl., Block 15, Lots 1 to 20 incl., Block 14, Lots 25 to 44 incl., Block 22, Lots 5 to 24 incl., Block 23, located on both sides of Cloverdale St. from 7th Ave. So. to 10th Ave. So. excepting BN zone at 8th Ave. So. intersection, as Multiple Residence Low Density (RM) Zone.
